These are Puzzles for 2x7 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-1::.
The people have 7 different jobs:  librarian, fisherman, coach, architect, chef, dressmaker, lawyer
There are 7 different nationalities: german, polish, pakistani, brazilian, malaysian, spanish, french
 1. the architect is on the left of the brazilian##1
 2. the malaysian is the architect##1
 3. the lawyer is on the right of the dressmaker##1
 4. the pakistani is on the right of the spanish##1
 5. the coach is in the middle##1
 6. the german is on the far left##1
 7. the chef is the german##1
 8. the librarian is on the right of the spanish##1
 9. the pakistani is on the left of the polish##1
10. the brazilian is on the left of the coach##1
11. the lawyer is on the right of the polish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2     |      3       |    4     |      5      |       6       |      7       |
| Job           | chef | architect | fisherman | coach | librarian | dressmaker | lawyer |
| Nationality   | german    | malaysian   | brazilian      | spanish | pakistani    | polish    | french         |

