.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-2::.
There 7 different types of food: pomegranate, pepper, carrot, artichoke, corn, lime, pear
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: house, folk, trance, country, reggae, dubstep, disco
 1. the fan of reggae is the person eating artichoke##1
 2. the person eating lime is on the left of the fan of disco##1
 3. the fan of dubstep is on the far right##1
 4. the person eating pepper is on the right of the fan of folk##1
 5. the person eating artichoke is on the right of the fan of country##1
 6. the person eating lime is on the left of the person eating pear##1
 7. the fan of reggae is in the middle##1
 8. the fan of reggae is on the right of the person eating corn##1
 9. the fan of disco is on the left of the person eating carrot##1
10. the person eating artichoke is on the left of the fan of house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |   3   |     4     |     5     |     6      |    7     |
| Food          | pomegranate | pepper | corn | artichoke | lime | pear | carrot |
| Music-Genre   | folk      | trance   | country   | reggae      | house       | disco       | dubstep     |

