.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-3::.
There 7 different types of food: pineapple, grapefruit, grapes, cranberry, pumpkin, orange, radish
The people have 7 different jobs:  librarian, dancer, manager, designer, accountant, paramedic, security-guard
 1. the person eating grapefruit is on the left of the person eating pumpkin##1
 2. the person eating pumpkin is on the left of the security-guard##1
 3. the dancer is on the left of the person eating radish##1
 4. the person eating pineapple is on the right of the person eating orange##1
 5. the librarian is the person eating pumpkin##1
 6. the manager is on the right of the dancer##1
 7. the dancer is on the left of the manager##1
 8. the dancer is on the right of the designer##1
 9. the person eating orange is the designer##1
10. the person eating grapes is on the right of the librarian##1
11. the designer is in the middle##1
12. the person eating radish is on the left of the accountant##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |    1     |     2     |   3    |      4       |     5      |    6     |     7     |
| Food   | grapefruit | pumpkin     | grapes  | orange       | pineapple       | radish  | cranberry   |
| Job    | paramedic  | librarian | security-guard | designer | dancer | manager | accountant |

