.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-4::.
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: techno, house, d&b, hip-hop, country, trance, electronic
There are 7 different nationalities: malaysian, chinese, japanese, colombian, brazilian, canadian, american
 1. the fan of country is the chinese##1
 2. the fan of electronic is on the right of the fan of trance##1
 3. the canadian is on the right of the japanese##1
 4. the malaysian is on the right of the fan of country##1
 5. the fan of country is on the left of the fan of techno##1
 6. the fan of trance is on the far left##1
 7. the japanese is on the right of the fan of trance##1
 8. the fan of d&b is on the right of the canadian##1
 9. the fan of d&b is the brazilian##1
10. the brazilian is on the left of the fan of house##1
11. the american is the fan of house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |    3     |     4      |  5   |     6      |     7     |
| Music-Genre   | trance    | electronic     | hip-hop     | d&b      | house | country      | techno     |
| Nationality   | colombian | japanese | canadian | brazilian | american | chinese | malaysian |

