.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-5::.
The people have 7 different hobbies: puzzles, reading, hiking, dancing, collecting, chess, woodworking
7 different pets are kept: goat, chinchilla, lizard, rabbit, hedgehog, hamster, cat
 1. the person who's hobby is reading is the owner of the cat##1
 2. the owner of the chinchilla is on the right of the person who's hobby is collecting##1
 3. the owner of the hamster is in the middle##1
 4. the owner of the hedgehog is on the right of the owner of the lizard##1
 5. the owner of the hedgehog is the person who's hobby is chess##1
 6. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the right of the owner of the goat##1
 7. the owner of the hamster is on the left of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
 8. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the right of the person who's hobby is reading##1
 9. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the right of the owner of the hedgehog##1
10. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |    2    |     3      |     4     |      5      |      6       |      7      |
| Hobby   | reading | hiking | chess     | dancing | woodworking | collecting | puzzles |
| Pet     | cat   | lizard    | hedgehog | hamster     | goat         | rabbit     | chinchilla        |

