.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-6::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: lemonade, milk, tea, water, hot-chocolate, fanta, cola
The people use 7 different means of transport: snowmobile, airplane, car, train, taxi, helicopter, motorbike
 1. the person drinking fanta is on the right of the person driving the train##1
 2. the person drinking lemonade is the person driving the snowmobile##1
 3. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the right of the person driving the airplane##1
 4. the person driving the snowmobile is on the left of the person driving the helicopter##1
 5. the person driving the motorbike is on the right of the person drinking cola##1
 6. the person drinking fanta is on the left of the person drinking lemonade##1
 7. the person drinking water is in the middle##1
 8. the person drinking tea is on the left of the person driving the taxi##1
 9. the person drinking milk is on the right of the person driving the motorbike##1
10. the person drinking tea is on the left of the person drinking fanta##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |     2      |  3  |    4     |    5    |   6   |      7      |
| Beverage    | tea | fanta   | lemonade | water | cola  | hot-chocolate | milk |
| Transport   | train   | taxi | snowmobile | helicopter     | airplane | motorbike | car   |

