.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-7::.
The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: comedy, horror, epic, documentary, thriller, family, disaster
The people use 7 different means of transport: taxi, bus, quad-bike, tram, subway, bike, car
 1. the person watching family movies is on the left of the person driving the bus##1
 2. the person watching documentary movies is on the left of the person watching thriller movies##1
 3. the person watching disaster movies is the person driving the tram##1
 4. the person driving the subway is on the left of the person watching horror movies##1
 5. the person watching family movies is on the right of the person driving the quad-bike##1
 6. the person driving the car is on the left of the person driving the quad-bike##1
 7. the person driving the taxi is the person watching epic movies##1
 8. the person watching thriller movies is in the middle##1
 9. the person driving the car is on the right of the person watching disaster movies##1
10. the person driving the taxi is on the right of the person watching horror movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |   3   |      4       |     5      |     6     |   7   |
| Movie-Genre   | comedy  | disaster | documentary | thriller | family     | horror | epic |
| Transport     | bike | tram      | car | quad-bike    | subway | bus   | taxi  |

