 6. the person who's hobby is singing is the person driving the bus##1
 7. the person who's hobby is reading is on the left of the person driving the motorbike##1
 8. the person driving the trike is on the right of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
 9. the person who's hobby is reading is in the middle##1
10. the person who's hobby is singing is on the right of the person who's hobby is collecting##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |     2     |      3      |       4       |     5      |     6      |    7    |
| Hobby       | fishing   | magic-tricks | cooking | reading | collecting     | singing | drawing |
| Transport   | jet-ski | ship      | trike        | subway         | motorbike | bus     | bike |

